                  <div className="mt-4 p-4 rounded-md bg-muted/50">
                    <h4 className="font-medium mb-2">代码抽取规则</h4>
                    <ul className="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
                      <li>• 共抽取 60 页（前30页 + 后30页）</li>
